Package: bootStat
Type: Package
Title: Bootstrap Interface for Descriptive Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Piotr Tymoszuk <piotr.s.tymoszuk@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides an easy to use functional interface to 
    compute bootstraped menas, standard deviations, quantiles and 
    confidence intervals for virtually any function computing descriptive 
    metrics of a numeric vector or a data frame.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
